org.franca.core.franca

Interface FArrayType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FModelElement, FType, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FArrayTypeImpl

    public interface FArrayType
extends FType
    A representation of the model object 'FArray Type'. This class represents an array type in Franca. The array type is used for defining an explicitly named type which represents an array of a given element type.

    The following features are supported:

    • Element Type

    See Also:
